But Liberty assumes only one shape, Once convinced that each of the molecules
which compose a fluid possesses in itself the force by which the general
level is produced, we conclude that there is no surer or simpler way
of seeing that level realized than not to interfere with it, All, then,
who set out with this fundamental principle, that men’s interests are
harmonious, will agree as to the practical solution of the social
problem, -- to abstain from displacing or thwarting these interests.
